  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_4405-4439",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4405-4439",
      "markText": "眼光长远是理性的，但也是苦闷的，因为美好永远在将来，当下永远有苦难。",
      "totalCount": 2006,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4405&rangeEnd=4439",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4405&rangeEnd=4439"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_1_1492-1526",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1492-1526",
      "markText": "科学与宗教的关系从来都是水火不容，社会稳定与个人自由的关系也是如此。",
      "totalCount": 1768,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1492&rangeEnd=1526",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1492&rangeEnd=1526"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_1_180-264",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "180-264",
      "markText": "哲学是介于神学与科学之间的东西。它与神学的共同之处在于，都包含着人类对未知事物的思考；它与科学也有共同之处，那就是理性地看待事物，而不是一切都遵循权威，无论是哪种权威。",
      "totalCount": 1232,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=180&rangeEnd=264",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=180&rangeEnd=264"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_1_711-738",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "711-738",
      "markText": "哲学的任务便是研究这样的问题，不过只是研究而不是解决。",
      "totalCount": 1152,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=711&rangeEnd=738",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=711&rangeEnd=738"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_22929-22961",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "22929-22961",
      "markText": "雅典迅速繁荣昌盛起来，财富和贸易增加了，道德和信仰必然就衰退了。",
      "totalCount": 1036,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=22929&rangeEnd=22961",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=22929&rangeEnd=22961"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_1_1167-1222",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "1167-1222",
      "markText": "怎样让人们在不回避的情况下，安心地在这些问题面前生活下去，并不受困扰，这就是哲学能为那些学哲学的人所作的事情。",
      "totalCount": 984,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1167&rangeEnd=1222",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=1167&rangeEnd=1222"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_1_450-481",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "450-481",
      "markText": "我们承认自然规律存在是不是因为人类骨子里有一种热爱秩序的天性？",
      "totalCount": 864,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=450&rangeEnd=481",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=450&rangeEnd=481"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_8_2035-2073",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2035-2073",
      "markText": "他认为没人会明知故犯，所以犯罪的根源就是无知，因此人们的品德离不开知识滋养。",
      "totalCount": 792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2035&rangeEnd=2073",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2035&rangeEnd=2073"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_16018-16054",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "16018-16054",
      "markText": "世界类似于一个岩洞，我们躲在洞内窥探着外面，只能看到现实世界的各种阴影。",
      "totalCount": 770,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=16018&rangeEnd=16054",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=16018&rangeEnd=16054"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_8954-9028",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "8954-9028",
      "markText": "他建立了一种宗教，教义主要是灵魂的轮回和吃豆子有罪。他的教徒成立宗教团体，并最终取得了一些地区的统治权。但是最后遭到人民反叛的原因是他们渴望吃豆子。",
      "totalCount": 768,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8954&rangeEnd=9028",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=8954&rangeEnd=9028"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_11755-11849",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "11755-11849",
      "markText": "赫拉克利特的学说偏重神秘主义，但是又不同于一般的神秘主义。他认为世界万物的本质都是火，火能毁掉一切，也能塑造一切。他还认为世界是对立统一的，一切产生于一，一生万物，一是万物之源，一就是神。",
      "totalCount": 697,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=11755&rangeEnd=11849",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=11755&rangeEnd=11849"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_1_6193-6251",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "6193-6251",
      "markText": "过分讲究纪律和遵循传统会导致社会僵化；而过分倡导自由主义与个人主义又会导致社会不团结，容易内部解体，或者被外族消灭。",
      "totalCount": 689,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6193&rangeEnd=6251",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=6193&rangeEnd=6251"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_1_4807-4827",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "4807-4827",
      "markText": "真理不需要权威机构确认，只需要内心肯定。",
      "totalCount": 636,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=4807&rangeEnd=4827",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=4807&rangeEnd=4827"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_9454-9475",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9454-9475",
      "markText": "真正的数学家是会像享受音乐一样享受数学的。",
      "totalCount": 616,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9454&rangeEnd=9475",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9454&rangeEnd=9475"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_12370-12456",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "12370-12456",
      "markText": "前人中泰勒斯认为世界的元素是水、阿那克西美尼认为世界的元素是气、赫拉克利特则认为世界的元素是火，最后的恩培多克勒的观点有点和解的意思，他认为世界的元素有土、气、火、水四种。",
      "totalCount": 592,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12370&rangeEnd=12456",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12370&rangeEnd=12456"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_12772-12810",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "12772-12810",
      "markText": "你不能两次踏入同一条河流；因为水不断地在流。 每天的太阳都是新的。",
      "totalCount": 561,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12772&rangeEnd=12810",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=12772&rangeEnd=12810"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_3_14722-14780",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "14722-14780",
      "markText": "如果一个观点在哲学上是正确的，那它在被驳倒后，会以其他形式重新站起来。并且被驳倒次数越多，这个观点将越精炼、越正确。",
      "totalCount": 559,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=14722&rangeEnd=14780",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=14722&rangeEnd=14780"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "184073_8_14866-14944",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "14866-14944",
      "markText": "一个假说，只要它能推动人们对一件事物的认识，无论事后被证明有多荒谬，它都是有用的；但是推动人们对这件事物的认识之后，这个假说便成为了这件事物继续前进的阻碍。",
      "totalCount": 559,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=184073&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14866&rangeEnd=14944",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3343271052cf09334242116?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14866&rangeEnd=14944"
    },
    {
